pageContext.quote: At a certain point in time, you go, “How much fucking sand is left in thisgoddamned hour glass? What are we doing with it?” You know? Are we on acontinued path of improvement and spiritual enlightenment, or do weeventually go, “Hey, guys, there’s a cliff coming up. Let’s just have adrink. There’s a fucking cliff. There’s a cliff right over there. We’reboth looking at it.”
